+         * "Mod": Mode: Auto: 0, Cool: 1, Dry: 2, Fan: 3, Heat: 4
+         * "SetTem": Requested Temperature
+         * "WdSpd": Fan Speed : Low:1, Medium Low:2, Medium :3, Medium High :4, High :5
+         * "Air": Air Mode Enabled
+         * "Blo": Dry
